high_descs: Walk over to the coffee table, then turn left and walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk up to the black shelf.
Pick up the blue credit card that is to the left of the blue vase on the black shelf.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a left and walk up to the black bench.
Put the credit card in the cardboard box that is on the bench.
Pick up the cardboard box with the credit card in it.
Turn left and walk to the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the black chair in the corner of the room.
Put the cardboard box with the credit card in it on the seat of the black chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with a credit card in it on the seat of a black chair.

high_descs: Walk ahead and a bit left to the shelves in the corner.
Pick up the credit card on the top shelf.
Look down.
Put the credit card in the box on the bottom shelf.
Pick up the box.
Turn around and walk to the chair in the right corner of the room.
Place the box on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Place a box on a chair.

high_descs: Walk to the shelves to the left of the television and look up at the top shelf.
Pick up the credit card to the left of the blue vase.
Move to the open box on the right side of the bottom shelf.
Put the credit card inside of the box.
Pick up the box from the shelf.
Turn around and walk to the black chair across the room to the right of the door.
Put the box down on the chair.
anns.task_desc: To put a credit card inside a box, and put the box on the black chair.

high_descs: Walk forward, turn left and walk towards the black chair, then turn right and walk to the black table with the white teapot.
Pick up the blue credit card from the overhead shelf next to the blue vase.
Turn right, walk forward, turn left to face the cardboard box on the black table.
Place blue credit card in the cardboard box on the black table.
Pick up the cardboard box on the black table.
Turn left, then turn left again, walk across the room to the black chair
Put the cardboard box on the black chair.
anns.task_desc: Put the credit card in a cardboard box.

high_descs: Walk over to the bench with the tea pot.
Pick up the credit card from the bench.
Turn right and walk to the open box at the other end of the bench.
Put the card inside the open box.
Pick up the box from the bench
Turn around and carry the box to the chair on the other side of the room.
Put the box on the seat of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a credit card inside onto the chair.

high_descs: Walk towards the bench and look up on the shelf.
Pick the credit card from the shelf.
Turn right, walk towards the box on the bench, and face the box.
Place the card in the box.
Pick up the box with the card from the bench.
Turn around and walk towards the sofa chair.
Place the box on the sofa chair.
anns.task_desc: Place the box with the credit card on the sofa chair.
